<br>
2) Conditions, this is more based on Moria. Most Moria swarm decks require mass amounts of conditions to pull of swarms often and consistently. <br>
<br>
Moria conditions are great! Swarms, Goblin Armory, They are comming, Wow! all fo them good, but not necesesarily needed. Moria is 8/10 times actuually one of the LEAST rare intensive deck types. Look at some of the decks posted ie "Look ma No Rares!", "Budget Swarm", or even some of the articles "How to make a competitive LOTR deck without selling you&#39;re first born" and "Building a Deck with No Rares and a List of Rares You Should Trade For When You Start". <br>
